          - fp16 small bs: ratio 0.19–0.28 → DataLoader marginal
          - fp16 大 bs (64+): ratio 0.32–0.56 → balanced, worth trying
        關鍵發現：WSI Pipeline bottleneck summary 顯示 encode 只佔 15–40%，
                 extract（openslide read_region）才佔 46–79%
        → 不採用 DataLoader；優化重心應轉向 extract（region caching / async read）

